==Tagnawt==
Tagnawt deg tɣiwant-agi d tin yeḥman daɣen tekkaw deg unebdu, d tasemmaḍt s waṭas n ugeffur deg tegrest.

==Amezruy==
Ṣaḥriǧ tella ur tt-zedɣen ara send ttṛad n 1954, imezdaɣ-is llan akk deg tuddar i s-d-yezzin, am At Walban, Iɣẓeṛ Iwaquṛen, Tagemmunt n At Laḥbib, Iɣil Ḥemmad, Ibelbaren, At Ɛli Utmim, Ɛeggac … d tiyaḍ, maca seg wakken i d-llant aṭas n tegrawliwin deg yidurar i d-yezzin, daɣen seg wakken i sen-tewɛeṛ tudert i yiṛumiyen akken ad d-ṭṭfen imjahden i yellan tefren deg tuddar-agi, d ayen i ten-yeǧǧan ad seṛɣen akk tuddar-agi, t-a deffir tayeḍ, ma d imezdaɣ-nsent ttwagaǧen-d ɣer Ṣaḥriǧ. Am akken i llant akk talliyin deg tegrawliwin, igad akk i d-iffɣen mgal acengu ttwadefṛen s tufka n ufus n imezdaɣ-nniḍen i teɣleb tugda, laɣcic neɣ ahat d tiririt n ttaṛ.

